<HEAD>Meese Says He Would Have Handled Wedtech Role Differently</HEAD>
<NOTE>EDs: Reworks throughout to include Meese's comment that he will
seek reimbursement for legal fees and additional background</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By PETE YOST</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
